<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_420" id="209v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_420_r2l1"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Hanſe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Truchſeʒʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Bald<ex>er</ex>ſh<ex>eim</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_420_r2l2">vogt cʒü <expan>vvinſh<ex>eim</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_420_r2l3"><expan>Lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> her Hans / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Hanſe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_420_r2l4">Stöckleins <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> / . Alſo <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir ſein rede <expan>v<ex>er</ex>hört</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_420_r2l5">Nu ſagt er von lewten / die nu langſte <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> todes <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_420_r2l6"><expan>abgange<ex>n</ex></expan> ſein / . daʒ wir / Jm nicht <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> darauff cʒe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_420_r2l8"><expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan> <expan>wıſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> / . Dann het 
<del rend="strikethrough"> er cʒü 
<add><ab facs="#facs_420_r2l7">
<del rend="strikethrough">an </del></ab></add> <expan>dheine<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_420_r2l9">
<del rend="strikethrough">ıht <expan>cʒevord<ex>er</ex>n</expan> gehabt / . </del> Jm <expan>dhein<ex>er</ex></expan> der <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ıht getan </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_420_r2l10">wenn er es dann an vns <expan>geuord<ex>er</ex>t</expan> het / ſo <expan>hett<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_420_r2l11">
<add><ab facs="#facs_420_r1l1">
<del rend="strikethrough">die </del></ab></add> wir Jm von den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex>s</expan> geholffen / . </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_420_r2l12">Auch <expan>w<ex>er</ex>es</expan> / daʒ er dheinen <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> die noch <expan>leb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_420_r2l13">noch ıht . beſchuldıgt / . So <expan>wolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir Jm von den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_420_r2l14"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> noch <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> frewntlıchs <expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>helffe<ex>n</ex></expan> / wenn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_420_r2l15">er das <expan>vord<ex>er</ex>t</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> ſo die vnd wir </del> ſo die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> an </del> die er </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_420_r2l16">vns benant anheim <expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_420_r2l19">Dewcht Jn <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> daʒ er cʒü vns ıht <expan>cʒeſpreche<ex>n</ex></expan> het / </ab><ab facs="#facs_420_r2l20"><expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir Jm auch frewntlıchs <expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_420_r2l21"><expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> ſein / an den <expan>ſtet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / da wir es <expan>pillıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tün </ab><ab facs="#facs_420_r2l22">ſüllen </ab></add> / vnd <expan>getr<ex>awen</ex></expan> <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_420_r2l17">wol / Jr weıſt Jn / daʒ er ſich daran <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> vns <expan>benüge<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_420_r2l18">laſſe vnd wo etc <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> vȷ̃ . <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>Re<ex>min</ex>ıſce<ex>re</ex></expan> / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_420" id="209v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Hanse<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Truchsezze<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Bald<ex>er</ex>sh<ex>eim</ex></expan>, vogt czü
                                <expan>Winsh<ex>eim</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> her Hans, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Hanse<ex>n</ex></expan> Stöckleins <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                        also <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir sein rede
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>hört</expan>; nu sagt er von lewten, die nu langste
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> todes <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>abgange<ex>n</ex></expan> sein, daz wir im nicht
                                <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> darauff cze
                            <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan>
<expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan>, dann het im <expan>dhein<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        der <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> iht getan, wenn er es dann an uns
                                <expan>gevord<ex>er</ex>t</expan> het, so
                            <expan>hett<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir im von den
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>
<expan>rechte<ex>n</ex>s</expan> geholffen. Auch
                            <expan>w<ex>er</ex>es</expan>, daz er dheinen
                            <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, die noch <expan>leb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> noch
                        iht beschuldigt, so <expan>wolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir im von den
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> noch <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>
                        frewntlichs <expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>helffe<ex>n</ex></expan>, wenn er das
                        <expan>vord<ex>er</ex>t</expan>, so die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, die
                        er uns benant, anheim <expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan>. <add>Dewcht in
                                    <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>, daz er czü uns iht <expan>cze
                                    spreche<ex>n</ex></expan> het, <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir im auch frewntlichs
                                    <expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> sein an den
                            <expan>stet<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, da wir es
                                <expan>pillich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tün süllen</add>; und
                                <expan>getr<ex>awen</ex></expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> wol, ir weist in, daz er sich daran
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> uns <expan>benüge<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        lasse. Und wo etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>re<ex>min</ex>isce<ex>re</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
